Key.Original: Arma 3 Revolución is an expansion to Arma 3 Aegis bringing new factions hailing from South America. Revolución brings players to the South American nation of Baracas, which teeters on the precipice between CSAT and NATO. The Defense Forces of Baracas face off against Socialist Revolutionary Armed Forces paramilitaries and their Venezuelan CSAT backers, all the while local Cartels run rampant.

Key.Turkish: Arma 3 Aegis aims to expand on the vanilla 2035 setting directly with a variety of new weapons, factions, vehicles, and equipment. Many items have been readded from the pre-Alpha, with a focus on bringing them up to the same level of quality and consistency as other vanilla items. Aegis also enhances the vanilla sandbox by improving vanilla faction's loadouts and visuals.
